General.Name: Yesil Yatirim Holding AS
General.Description: Yesil Yatirim Holding Anonim Sirketi provides technical planning, programming, budgeting, and project planning services related to financial markets. The company also offers real estate valuation services; and investment and research services in the commercial, industrial, and financial areas. In addition, it offers company valuation services. The company is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.
